{"id":1196,"date":"2018-08-02T15:49:10","date_gmt":"2018-08-02T19:49:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1196"},"modified":"2023-06-12T12:04:50","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T16:04:50","slug":"genevieve-richer","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/genevieve-richer\/","title":{"rendered":"Genevi\u00e8ve Richer"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Genevi\u00e8ve Richer enseigne au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent depuis 2003. C\u2019est dans le cadre de sa ma\u00eetrise en \u00e9tudes litt\u00e9raires (UQAM, 2001) et de son m\u00e9moire sur l\u2019\u0153uvre d\u2019Alessandro Baricco qu\u2019elle b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiera d\u2019un stage d\u2019\u00e9tudes, \u00e0 l\u2019Universit\u00e9 de Florence, qui confirmera son amour de la litt\u00e9rature italienne, mais aussi sa fascination pour l\u2019influence des arts en g\u00e9n\u00e9ral sur l\u2019\u00e9criture et la litt\u00e9rature de toutes les \u00e9poques.<\/p>\n<p>Dans son enseignement, elle cherche \u00e0 partager avec enthousiasme son int\u00e9r\u00eat pour la lecture, la pens\u00e9e et l\u2019imaginaire. Elle aime bien l\u2019id\u00e9e qu\u2019on ne fasse pas tous le m\u00eame voyage en lisant un m\u00eame livre.<\/p>\n<p>Citation pr\u00e9f\u00e9r\u00e9e\u00a0:<\/p>\n<p>Les familles heureuses se ressemblent toutes; les familles malheureuses sont malheureuses chacune \u00e0 leur fa\u00e7on.<\/p>\n<p>L\u00e9on Tolsto\u00ef,\u00a0<em>Anna Kar\u00e9nine<\/em>, 1877<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1197,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[214],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1196","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-francais"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1196","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1197"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1196"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"categorie-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categorie-equipe?post=1196"},{"taxonomy":"departement-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/departement-equipe?post=1196"},{"taxonomy":"specialite-equipe","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/specialite-equipe?post=1196"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiquette-interne?post=1196"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}